---
import MainGridLayout from "../layouts/MainGridLayout.astro";
import I18nKey from "../i18n/i18nKey";
import { i18n } from "../i18n/translation";
---

<MainGridLayout title={i18n(I18nKey.about)} description="朱昊的双语简介、联系方式和当前状态。">
	<section data-about-switcher class="card-base overflow-hidden rounded-[var(--radius-large)] px-6 py-6 md:px-8 md:py-7">
		<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
			<div>
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-[var(--primary)]">About</p>
				<h1 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50">关于我</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="flex rounded-xl bg-black/5 p-1 dark:bg-white/10" role="tablist" aria-label="About language switch">
				<button id="about-zh-btn" type="button" data-about-lang="zh" class="about-tab-btn rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold" aria-selected="true" data-active="true">中文</button>
				<button id="about-en-btn" type="button" data-about-lang="en" class="about-tab-btn rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold" aria-selected="false" data-active="false">English</button>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
			<div id="about-zh" data-about-panel="zh" class="space-y-4">
				<p>你好，我是朱昊。最近刚走完本科阶段，马上毕业，现在是北京电子科技学院研零。</p>
				<p>我更喜欢把自己的经历写清楚一点，所以这里会放保研、项目、读书和一些真正有用的记录。内容可能不多，但会尽量真实、直接。</p>
				<div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 dark:border-white/10">
						<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">现在在做</div>
						<p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">整理保研回忆贴，补项目笔记，顺手把网站继续写顺。</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 dark:border-white/10">
						<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">关注方向</div>
						<p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">AI 系统、内容真实性、MCP/RAG、工程化流程。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-2">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-500">联系我</p>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm">
						<a class="link-underline" href="https://github.com/dcygtheshy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
						<a class="link-underline" href="mailto:1633960501@qq.com">Email</a>
						<a class="link-underline" href="/rss.xml">RSS</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="about-en" data-about-panel="en" class="space-y-4 hidden">
				<p>Hi, I am Zhu Hao. I am finishing my undergraduate degree and will start graduate school at Beijing Electronic Science and Technology Institute.</p>
				<p>This site is where I keep a clear record of things that matter to me: my grad-school application journey, small projects, notes, and the bits of life around them. I try to keep the writing honest and practical.</p>
				<div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
					<div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 dark:border-white/10">
						<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Now</div>
						<p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">Wrapping up the bachelor's chapter and preparing for the next one.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="rounded-xl border border-black/10 p-4 dark:border-white/10">
						<div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Interests</div>
						<p class="mt-2 text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">AI systems, content authenticity, MCP/RAG, and engineering workflows.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<style>
		.about-tab-btn {
			color: var(--tw-prose-body);
		}
		.about-tab-btn[data-active="true"] {
			background: var(--primary);
			color: white;
		}
	</style>
</MainGridLayout>
